# ==============================================================================
# OPTIMIZATION NOTES
# ==============================================================================
# This .dockerignore file is optimized for:
# 1. Smaller Docker image sizes
# 2. Faster Docker builds
# 3. Excluding development-only files
# 4. Security (no secrets in images)
# 5. Only including necessary runtime files
#
# For production builds, only essential files are included:
# - Package.json (for dependencies)
# - Built application code
# - Necessary configuration files
# - Runtime assets
# ==============================================================================


